    "rich_text_gcMpbN": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "subheading_qNTHT3": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "MUMU BATH WHERE AVOCADO MEETS LUXURY"
          }
        },
        "heading_gxFG7j": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Avocado Soaps Collection by Mumu Bath",
            "heading_tag": "h2"
          }
        },
        "richtext_efx6yy": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Our avocado oil soaps are crafted to deeply hydrate, calm, and restore balance to your skin. Packed with vitamins and antioxidants, they’re perfect for all skin types - even the most <a>sensitive</a>.</p><p>Gentle yet effective, each bar is made with love using our signature <strong>soap avocado</strong> blend. Experience the lush, creamy lather that leaves your skin soft, refreshed, and glowing.</p><h2>Why Choose Our Avocado Soap?</h2><p>Our range of avocado soaps are meticulously handcrafted using a blend of olive and coconut oils, enriched with the luxurious addition of avocado oil. This unique combination offers:</p><ul><li><strong>Deep Hydration for Dry Skin</strong>: The natural oils work together to moisturize and soothe even the driest skin types.</li><li><strong>Gentle Cleansing</strong>: Experience a pleasant, foaming lather that cleanses effectively without stripping your skin of its natural oils.</li><li><strong>Skin Protection</strong>: Avocado oil helps create a protective barrier, minimizing irritation and inflammation.</li><li><strong>Antimicrobial Properties</strong>: Thanks to the lauric acid in avocado oil, our soaps offer natural antimicrobial benefits.</li><li><strong>Potential Acne Prevention</strong>: By keeping your skin properly protected and reducing irritation, our avocado soaps may help prevent breakouts.</li></ul><h2>Our Avocado Oil Infused Soaps</h2><p>Explore our diverse range of avocado oil-enriched soaps, each offering a unique sensory experience:</p><p><a href=\"https://www.mumubath.com/products/mt-ali-taiwanese-tea-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"mt ali taiwanese tea soap with avocado iol\">Mt. Ali Taiwanese Tea Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/orange-eucalyptus-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Yuzu Eucalyptus Soap\">Yuzu Eucalyptus Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/earth-sea-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Earth & Sea Soap\">Earth & Sea Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/rose-pink-clay-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Rose Pink Clay Soap\">Rose Pink Clay Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/mango-turmeric-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Mango Turmeric Soap\">Mango Turmeric Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/goji-berry-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Goji Berry Jujube Soap\">Goji Berry Jujube Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/new-yorker-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"New Yorker Soap\">New Yorker Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/cherry-blossom-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Cherry Blossom Soap\">Cherry Blossom Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/central-park-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Central Park Soap\">Central Park Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/city-cafe-coffee-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"City Cafe Coffee Soap\">City Cafe Coffee Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/matcha-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Matcha Soap Bar\">Matcha Soap Bar</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/honeysuckle-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Honeysuckle Soap\">Honeysuckle Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/brooklyn-bridge\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Brooklyn Bridge Soap\">Brooklyn Bridge Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/rainbow-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Rainbow Soap\">Rainbow Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/yellow-cab-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Yellow Cab Soap\">Yellow Cab Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/dumbo-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Dumbo soap\">Dumbo Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/big-apple-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Big Apple Soap\">Big Apple Soap</a></p><p><a href=\"/products/coconut-pineapple-soap\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Coconut & Pineapple Soap Bar\">Coconut & Pineapple Soap Bar</a></p><h2>Nourish Your Skin Naturally with Our Avocado Soap</h2><p>Each soap bar in our collection combines the nourishing properties of avocado oil with unique ingredients and fragrances, offering a luxurious bathing experience while caring for your skin.</p><p>Treat your skin to the natural goodness of avocado with Mumu Bath's Avocado Soaps Collection. Experience the difference that handcrafted, oil-rich soaps can make for your skin's health and appearance.</p><p></p><h2>How to Use Your <strong>Avocado Oil Soap</strong></h2><p> </p><p>Gentle and effective, our <strong>avocado oil soaps</strong> are easy<br/>to incorporate into your daily skincare. Follow these simple steps for the best<br/>results.</p><p><strong>1. Wet and Lather</strong><br/>– Rub the bar between your hands or on a loofah to create a rich lather. Apply<br/>to damp skin in circular motions.</p><p><strong>2. Cleanse Gently</strong><br/>– Let the creamy lather sit for a few seconds to nourish the skin. Then rinse<br/>thoroughly with warm water.</p><p><strong>3. Use on Face and Body</strong><br/>– Our <strong>soap avocado </strong>formula is safe for both facial and full-body cleansing.<br/>Use morning or night for soft, balanced skin.</p><p><strong>4. Store Properly</strong><br/>– Keep your bar dry between uses to make it last longer. Use a draining soap<br/>dish to prevent softening.</p><p> </p><h2>Why Shop from Us</h2><p><strong> </strong>We believe in creating skin-loving products with simple, safe,<br/>and effective ingredients. Our soaps are handcrafted to bring you nourishing<br/>care with a clean conscience.</p><p><strong>Clean, Natural Ingredients</strong> – We use only plant-based oils, essential oils, and natural<br/>additives - no synthetic nasties, ever. Your skin deserves the gentle touch of<br/>pure ingredients.</p><p><strong>Handcrafted with Care</strong> – Every bar is artisan-made in small batches to ensure<br/>freshness and quality. You’ll feel the difference from the first use.</p><p><strong>Versatile Skincare Options</strong> – From soothing bars to our hydrating <strong>avocado body wash</strong>,<br/>we offer products for every skin type. We’re here for your whole skincare<br/>routine.</p><p><strong>Eco-Friendly Packaging</strong> – Our soaps are wrapped in recyclable, minimal packaging.<br/>It’s our way of loving the planet while caring for your skin.</p><p><strong>Trusted by Families</strong> – Mumu Bath is a brand built on family values and honest<br/>craftsmanship. We create products we proudly use on our own loved ones.</p>"
          }
        }
